  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Europe.

      The aim of this observational study is to investigate the switch from metformin alone to
      metformin combined with repaglinide in type 2 diabetic patients not achieving adequate
      glycaemic control on maximal dose of metformin given alone and to analyse different
      epidemiological parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
